int main()
{
  x$w_buff1 = x$w_buff0;
  x$w_buff0 = 1;
  x$w_buff1_used = x$w_buff0_used;
  x$w_buff0_used = TRUE;
  x$r_buff1_thd0 = x$r_buff0_thd0;
  x$r_buff1_thd1 = x$r_buff0_thd1;
  x$r_buff1_thd2 = x$r_buff0_thd2;
  x$r_buff0_thd1 = TRUE;
  y = 1;
